  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House", 
    "date": "2015-07-29T04:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Community Bank Flexibility Act \n\nThis bill amends the Internal Revenue Code, with respect to the tax treatment of small banks, to: (1) allow such banks to reorganize as either corporations or partnerships for tax purposes, (2) permit such banks to reorganize without incurring an additional tax for liquidation, and (3) impose a five-year recognition period of the built-in gains of such banks."
  }, 
